The paper proposes a methodology for encoding programs using representation learning methods and flow analysis information. This methodology is applied to software engineering and optimization tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also deals with programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the use of flow analysis information suggests a potential application in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems (cs.SY).
